VTuber Schedule API - Documentation Repository

This repository contains public documentation for the VTuber Schedule API.
The API itself is a commercial service provided through RapidAPI.

For usage terms, please refer to the RapidAPI terms of service.

---

Documentation License

The documentation in this repository is provided for informational purposes.
You may reference and link to this documentation in your projects.

---

API Usage

To use the VTuber Schedule API, you must subscribe through RapidAPI:
https://rapidapi.com/luvgoel555/api/vtuber-schedule

API usage is subject to the terms of your RapidAPI subscription plan.